Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.67,OPcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}继续相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:47.43,OPcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}放眼未来 辉煌灿烂 Ooh ooh ooh ooh
